text: Rachel Campos-DuffyCampos-Duffy, Rachel (December 19, 2007). "I'm Expecting My 5th: What To Make Of The Trend In Bigger Families". Parent Dish. ( Campos; born October 22, 1971) is an American conservative television personality. She first appeared on television in 1994 as a cast member on the MTV reality television series The Real World: San Francisco. She was a guest host on the ABC talk show The View."Rachel Campos-Duffy". Fox News. Retrieved June 7, 2018. She also is a permanent co-host on Fox & Friends Weekend in May 2021. In 1999, she married Sean Duffy.
